cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.SI, cs.DC 

The paper deals with control of platoons of vehicles, which involves topics related to systems and control (cs.SY), mathematical analysis (cs.MA), robotics (cs.RO), signal processing (cs.SI), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The use of Laplacians and wave equations also suggests a connection to graph theory and numerical analysis, which are sub-fields of computer science. However, since the focus is on control and optimization of physical systems, cs.SY and cs.MA are the most likely categories.
